title: Building a Simple AWS CloudTrail Data Analytics Solution
content:
Building a Simple AWS CloudTrail Data Analytics Solution Overview In this lab, you will explore the fundamentals of Amazon VPC (Virtual Private Cloud) and AWS VPN (Virtual Private Network) Site-to-Site connections. Gain an understanding of essential concepts and features within Amazon VPC, and practice creating a basic VPC. Additionally, learn how to configure a Site-to-Site VPN to establish a connection between an on-premise environment and an AWS VPC environment.
